data.description: Urban living at its finest! This meticulously maintained 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home is located one mile from the Pearl, minutes from downtown, with close proximity to major highways. Modern interior w/ concrete floors, NEST thermostat. Primary suite is located downstairs; boasts a full bathroom, ceiling fan and a great sized closet! Cozy kitchen with plenty of cabinet and countertop space with recessed lighting. Open floor plan & lots of natural light. One-car garage + carport. Near great schools, shopping, and plenty of San Antonio attractions! As an added bonus the house comes fully furnished with everything you see!!
